# Flathub curation BLOCKLIST — force-exclude an app id even if it passes every
# automatic filter in svk-flathub-sync.py. Same shape as flathub-allowlist.example
# (and /etc/svk/flatpaks.list): one app id per line, '#' comments, blank lines
# ignored.
#
# Seeded to /var/lib/svk/flathub-blocklist on first run; edit the real file on
# the server, not this one.
#
# org.example.UnwantedApp
